  <summary date="2021-06-21T18:51:31Z" status="Introduced in House">Ending Punitive, Unfair, School-based Harm that is Overt and Unresponsive to Trauma Act of 2021 or the Ending PUSHOUT Act of 2021

This bill requires the Department of Education (ED)&#160;to award grants to local educational agencies and nonprofit organizations for the purpose of reducing suspension and expulsion of students (i.e., exclusionary disciplinary practices).

The bill requires ED&#160;to collect data on exclusionary discipline in schools.

It also establishes a joint task force to end school pushout.</summary>
